text: Mike Pence and Kamala Harris will be separated by 12 feet at their vice presidential debate on Wednesday, a source says. The decision comes after Joe Biden's campaign raised health concerns about the initial seven-feet distance planned at the seated debate https://t.co/MzA6eiJstS
